description:
"THE LONE RANGERS" *
Obra: Neo Barrio "LA DANTA"
Por: Gustavo Fajardo; Alejandro Najarro.

Welcome to LA DANTA street, a metaverse that mixes our mayan culture roots with our vision of a regional cyberpunk. We present a ritual of the shamans to ask us to connect with our roots, learn and being proud of them, and move on from it to a better future.
